prompts.frontCover: A vibrant and humorous watercolor painting for a birthday card front. The scene features a charmingly clumsy cartoon giraffe, painted in soft yellows and browns with delicate watercolor bleeds and soft edges. The giraffe is tangled hilariously in a string of colorful party bunting and is wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat. It has a slightly surprised and goofy expression on its face as it tries to nibble on a ridiculously large, multi-layered birthday cake that is tilting precariously. Pastel-colored confetti and whimsical splatters of watercolor paint float gently in the air against a clean, white background. In the center of the composition, written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Hope your birthday is wild!". The overall style is lighthearted, artistic, and flat 2D, perfect for a printed card.
